posting_body: ['AVAILABLE NOW -BRIGHT 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath w/Pool, Laundry, Includes Parking / Walk to Broadway Plaza!', 'Welcome to Casa Del Rio.', 'Our bright and airy 2 bedroom 1 bathroom apartment home is ready for you to call home!', 'This quaint 15 unit building has a pool for your enjoyment, washer and dryer on site, adn includes 1 assigned parking spot at no additional cost!', 'Close proximity to all Downtown Walnut Creek has to offer: shopping, eateries, and more!', 'Come take a look!', 'Wont last long.', 'UNIT + BUILDING FEATURES:', '- 18 unit building', '- Large 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath', '- Kitchen + Breakfast Nook: Includes a dishwasher, refrigerator, electric stovetop & oven w/engineered wood flooring', '- A/C in unit', '- Fireplace', '- Shared Pool', '- [INCLUDES] 1 Assigned parking space', '- Coin operated laundry on site', '- Carpet in living areas', "- Close to Walnut Creek's Downtown shopping and eateries", '- Easy access to HWY 24 and 680; alternate transportation nearby', 'LEASE TERMS:', 'Rental Amount: $2,250 (1 year lease)', 'Security Deposit: $2,250', 'Tenant Pays: PGE', 'Owner Pays: Water and Garbage', 'INCLUDES 1 assigned parking spot', '700+ credit score', 'Available Now!', 'CONTACT:', 'Chris, Resident Manager.', 'CALL/TEXT:', 'show contact info', '***PLEASE CONTACT CHRIS DIRECTLY***']
